o門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bcd1ee8cf3f17707430174d65b9d7e16e3ea9e0","tid":2032211,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"九龍新界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3036500504431ff9d1fe1d1931fc4a504d113dbc","tid":2032211,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"唔防火的垃圾一舊，浪費公帑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位，連登黑色五毛風向警告</span><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span><br />\n<br />\n再借個位<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n最後想請大家簽一簽以下聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.change.org%2Fp%2Fuk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=2913ff00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.change.org/p/uk-govt-uk-govt-introduce-alistair-carmichael-s-private-members-bill-on-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"900fefa8289c7817d13a64b73bd5d08df7b86c1b","tid":2032211,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔塞路無路障 佢地都冇用而D仆街車既資格"},{"pid":"149fe6286fd895cc9141e179aa3786b6c7d267f8","tid":2032211,"uid":32220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"水炮車姐成日都見驚條毛咩"},{"pid":"2e04759d32fe6fbe658b9e3dd6be8ab098712467","tid":2032211,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"久違警嫂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350c3924e7f0f1a553f73d9d3e605c3a4da5aa6c","tid":2032211,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"跟本擺晒d武器出黎嚇人"},{"pid":"fd285871809ac6b81b9384ad2d600331aebb70ae","tid":2032211,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900fefa8289c7817d13a64b73bd5d08df7b86c1b","tid":2032211,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔塞路無路障 佢地都冇用而D仆街車既資格"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"依D實有人做嫁啦"},{"pid":"b02d2bb06476610f7a1aacf306dfcb0484bf4348","tid":2032211,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:00:22.000Z","msg":"銳武廢架<br />\n<br />\n火魔二連擊可收皮"},{"pid":"de8f8b958a71221de1be5c89fa0509dead0eea0e","tid":2032211,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd285871809ac6b81b9384ad2d600331aebb70ae","tid":2032211,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"900fefa8289c7817d13a64b73bd5d08df7b86c1b","tid":2032211,"uid":105340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:53:05.000Z","msg":"唔塞路無路障 佢地都冇用而D仆街車既資格"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"依D實有人做嫁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"6789ca24cae240a2b4481e479bf298c6b53ca428","ti